. We will keep notifying you about all the new coupons you get but do visit your Snapbox section regularly.So, what next ?<br>Funda is simple. The more you shop, the more coupons you getâ€¦<br><br><br><b>Here are some answers to your queries</b><br><br>Ques: How do I redeem Snapbox Promo codes?Ans. Visit your Snapbox section regularly to checkout the latest offers. While making the purchase, we would provide you the option to choose from all the available promo codes. (Info graphic to be shown)<br><br>Ques How to find Snapbox promo codes while making purchase?Ans: Please log in first to and visit the order summary page. Snapbox promo code can be seen on bottom right as shown in image(Show Image)<br><br> Ques: How many Snapbox promo codes can be used at onceAns: Only one.<br><br>Ques: What is the notification icon?Ans: Notification icon would give alerts in case of arrival of new promo code, applicability of promo code in a particular category/PDP you are viewing.<br><br></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><img width=\"540\" height=\"13\" border=\"0\" /></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr><td><img width=\"167\" height=\"79\" border=\"0\" /></td><td><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/snapdeal\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Find Us on Facebook\" border=\"0\" /></a></td><td><a href=\"http://twitter.com/snapyourdeal\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Follow Us on Twitter\" border=\"0\" /></a></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td> </td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:10px 20px 10px 20px;\" align=\"center\"><table width=\"103\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr><td width=\"103\" align=\"center\"><img border=\"0\" /></td></tr><tr><td style=\"font-family:'Trebuchet MS'; font-size: 21px; font-weight: bold; color: #029dcb; text-align: center;\">Thankyou!</td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td align=\"center\" class=\"feel-txt\" style=\"background-color:#def7fb;padding:10px 20px 10px 20px;border-top:2px solid #b9f2fd;\">Still have questions? <a href=\"http://www.snapdeal.com/info/faq\" style=\"color:#000000; text-decoration:underline\">Check out the FAQ page</a><br /><br />Reach us at: SnapDeal.com, 246, First Floor, Okhla Phase III, New Delhi - 110020</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>" where `name` = "snapBoxActivationConfirmation";
